- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses deep learning methods for object tracking. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of AI techniques for visual tracking. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of the algorithm for mobile applications, which could include robotics.
